# ERIFY™ Image Spec 👑🔥

This repository is a fork of the [OCI Image Format Specification](https://github.com/opencontainers/image-spec).  
It is maintained and adapted for use in the **ERIFY App ecosystem**.

---

## 📌 Overview
The **OCI Image Format** defines an open standard for container images.  
This fork ensures compatibility with ERIFY Studio systems and provides space for extensions, experiments, and documentation aligned with our platform needs.

---

## 🚀 ERIFY Adaptations
- Branded integration with **ERIFY-App** workflows  
- Placeholder for future **OCI extensions** required by ERIFY infrastructure  
- Documentation improvements for internal developer use  

---

## 🤝 Contributing
This fork primarily serves ERIFY Studio needs.  
If you wish to contribute upstream, please open a PR on the official [opencontainers/image-spec](https://github.com/opencontainers/image-spec).

